01:57:13,836 --> 01:57:15,167
Am I lying to you?

259
01:57:24,513 --> 01:57:26,504
I met Pooja in a bus.

260
01:57:28,517 --> 01:57:32,248
We were together all the time
I fell in love with her.

261
01:57:34,523 --> 01:57:37,981
I love her
And she loves me.

262
01:57:39,528 --> 01:57:42,258
Right now I'm in a rush.
She must be waiting for me.

263
01:57:42,865 --> 01:57:45,527
She doesn't know I've
come to give you this news.

264
01:57:46,535 --> 01:57:49,470
Every minute is valuable.
And I have not a penny.

265
01:57:50,472 --> 01:57:53,873
''Under these circumstances, how
can I tell her I want to marry her? ''

266
01:57:58,480 --> 01:58:01,472
''Yes, there is a story.''

267
01:58:02,484 --> 01:58:04,145
