There was no such news.

342
02:07:33,188 --> 02:07:34,519
The flush doesn't work.

343
02:07:34,923 --> 02:07:37,915
Everyone cheats me of
my money. Money...?

344
02:07:38,527 --> 02:07:40,927
- Raghu returned it.
- Why?

345
02:07:41,530 --> 02:07:43,521
He said that was a lie.

346
02:07:44,533 --> 02:07:46,023
Where is he?

347
02:07:56,878 --> 02:07:59,472
What is this?

348
02:08:01,883 --> 02:08:03,874
Thought I'd pull your leg.

349
02:08:06,488 --> 02:08:08,149
But the story was good?

350
02:08:10,492 --> 02:08:12,892
It happens. This happens in life.

351
02:08:13,495 --> 02:08:15,895
Man plans something but
something else happens.

352
02:08:18,500 --> 02:08:22,231
Keep this. Get back when
you're in the mood. We'll talk.

353
02:08:58,740 --> 02:09:00,799
I knocked but you...

354
02:09:01,476 --> 02:09:02,966
I was thinking.

355
02:09:05,480 --> 02:09:09,814
Everything is arranged.
Your marriage is being talked.

356
02:09:11,486 --> 02:09:15,980
I hear Deepak will come in
a chopper for the wedding.

357
02:09:16,491 --> 02:09:17,890
I too heard that.

358
02:09:19,494 --> 02:09:22,895
It's madness according
to me but it's all right.

359
02:09:23,498 --> 02:09:25,489
He can do what he thinks is right.

360
02:09:37,512 --> 02:09:39,980
''Dear, what's wrong? ''

361
02:09:40,915 --> 02:09:42,906
- What is wrong?
- Nothing.

362
02:09:44,919 --> 02:09:48,446
You seem upset since you came.

363
02:09:49,457 --> 02:09:51,118
I'm worried abut you.

364
02:09:52,794 --> 02:09:55,456
Are the marriage preparations fine?

365
02:09:57,465 --> 02:09:59,126
Have Deepak and you...?

366
02:09:59,801 --> 02:10:05,467
- No. - If there's
something... it's not too late.

367
02:10:05,874 --> 02:10:08,468
Do you know my real
feelings about Deepak?

368
02:10:12,480 --> 02:10:13,913
My child...

369
02:10:16,484 --> 02:10:18,475
I want you to be happy.

370
02:10:19,888 --> 02:10:22,880
I want to give you
the world's happiness.

371
02:10:24,492 --> 02:10:25,959
What is the matter?

372
02:10:28,496 --> 02:10:29,895
My baby...

373
02:10:40,508 --> 02:10:43,238
Are you in love with another?

374
02:10:55,457 --> 02:10:57,448
Love! You love somebody else!

375
02:10:57,859 --> 02:10:59,451
Not Deepak? Fantastic!

376
02:11:00,462 --> 02:11:03,124
- Where did you meet him?
- In the bus.

377
02:11:03,865 --> 02:11:06,857
Bus...? Is he a bus conductor?

378
02:11:08,470 --> 02:11:11,462
- No.
- Who is he?

379
02:11:12,474 --> 02:11:17,207
I don't know much about him
but I like him.

380
02:11:17,979 --> 02:11:20,470
You like the bus or him?

381
02:11:21,483 --> 02:11:24,475
- Him.
- Then why are you serious?

382
02:11:25,487 --> 02:11:26,977
No use.

383
02:11:27,489 --> 02:11:29,150
He hates me!

384
02:11:30,892 --> 02:11:34,157
- Hates...? - He thinks I'm the
spoilt child of a rich father.

385
02:11:35,497 --> 02:11:37,488
Spoilt child of a rich man?

386
02:11:37,832 --> 02:11:39,163
He thinks something
similar about you too.

387
02:11:40,502 --> 02:11:42,493
He says you're
responsible for spoiling me.

388
02:11:42,837 --> 02:11:44,498
You didn't raise me well.

389
02:11:45,006 --> 02:11:46,496
Where is he?
I want to meet him.

390
02:11:46,841 --> 02:11:48,172
- I want to meet him.
- Don't know.

391
02:11:48,710 --> 02:11:52,111
I must meet him. It's urgent!
This wedding has to be stopped.

392
02:11:52,447 --> 02:11:54,438
Stop it. Stop!!

393
02:11:55,450 --> 02:11:57,441
- This marriage is wrong.
- Daddy...

394
02:11:58,453 --> 02:12:00,444
Send the groom back!

395
02:12:02,457 --> 02:12:04,448
I want the boy!

396
02:12:13,868 --> 02:12:15,460
I don't want to trouble you more.

397
02:12:16,871 --> 02:12:20,739
The boy was right. I kept
running around without thinking.

398
02:12:21,476 --> 02:12:22,966
What did I want?

399
02:12:23,478 --> 02:12:25,469
Now I must stop somewhere.

400
02:12:26,481 --> 02:12:28,073
I must hold somebody's hand.

401
02:12:31,486 --> 02:12:32,976
You've changed.

402
02:12:34,489 --> 02:12:36,150
You were a kid when
you bolted from the ship.

403
02:12:37,892 --> 02:12:40,486
But you've returned as a woman.

404
02:12:41,496 --> 02:12:43,487
This boy must have a hand in this.

405
02:12:43,998 --> 02:12:46,831
- The boy! I want the boy!
- You won't find Raghu now.

406
02:12:47,435 --> 02:12:49,426
Who won't be found?

407
02:12:51,840 --> 02:12:53,171
What's his full name?

408
02:13:03,785 --> 02:13:05,116
What is this?

409
02:13:05,453 --> 02:13:07,444
Nothing... no...

410
02:13:15,463 --> 02:13:20,059
''Mr. Dharamchand, I want to
talk to you about money.''

411
02:13:20,468 --> 02:13:22,459
Concerning your daughter.

412
02:13:27,475 --> 02:13:30,205
- Will you see him?
- I'll have to.

413
02:13:30,812 --> 02:13:33,940
He found you so I must reward him.

414
02:13:39,754 --> 02:13:42,746
Do meet him and don't
forget to reward him.

415
02:13:43,491 --> 02:13:45,482
He was good company
during the journey.

416
02:13:46,494 --> 02:13:48,155
And do tip him.

417
02:14:00,108 --> 02:14:01,439
Pooja...!

418
02:14:13,955 --> 02:14:15,946
- Where's Pooja?
- Upstairs.

419
02:14:24,799 --> 02:14:26,198
I've come to take you.

420
02:14:27,468 --> 02:14:30,130
Get dressed. We're
going to a grand party.

421
02:14:31,472 --> 02:14:33,463
''- You'll come, won't you?
- Yes.''

422
02:14:47,422 --> 02:14:49,890
What's wrong with you?
Why are you standing morose?

423
02:14:51,426 --> 02:14:53,826
Every year you're the life
of the party. What's it now?

424
02:14:54,028 --> 02:14:55,427
I'm not in the mood.

425
02:14:56,431 --> 02:14:59,889
''Forget it. At this age,
girls come and go.''

426
02:15:00,435 --> 02:15:02,835
''Lf one girl leaves, will
you mope all your life? ''

427
02:15:06,441 --> 02:15:10,434
Stand near the door and
receive all the guests.

428
02:16:04,999 --> 02:16:08,491
You are the love of one man

429
02:16:09,504 --> 02:16:13,497
But another man loves you

430
