432
02:16:23,851 --> 02:16:26,945
One man likes you

433
02:16:28,523 --> 02:16:31,959
One man likes you

434
02:16:32,927 --> 02:16:36,522
But somebody else wants you

435
02:17:05,493 --> 02:17:08,758
''What is ours and
what belongs to others''

436
02:17:09,897 --> 02:17:13,298
