Who in the world knows?

441
02:17:32,920 --> 02:17:36,515
You are in one man's vision

442
02:17:37,525 --> 02:17:41,518
But another steals glances

443
02:18:38,519 --> 02:18:41,511
This often happens in love

444
02:18:42,790 --> 02:18:46,248
''One laughs while
