''How can I bear the
pain in my heart? ''

455
02:20:28,496 --> 02:20:32,489
''How can I say
I'm facing a dilemma? ''

456
02:20:33,501 --> 02:20:36,834
''How can I say
I'm facing a dilemma? ''

457
02:20:37,905 --> 02:20:41,500
You are my only companion

458
02:20:42,510 --> 02:20:46,503
None other walks beside me

459
02:22:01,455 --> 02:22:02,854
''Yes, this is Raghu Jaitly''

460
02:22:05,459 --> 02:22:06,949
''No, I won't come home.''

461
02:22:08,462 --> 02:22:09,929
I want to meet you in the office.

462
02:22:11,465 --> 02:22:15,128
L; m going to Bombay in 2 days
Then I might go to America.

463
02:22:15,803 --> 02:22:18,795
''Before I leave, I want
to clear your account.''

464
02:22:19,473 --> 02:22:23,807
But I don't want to come
in the midst of the wedding.

465
02:22:24,478 --> 02:22:28,471
That's none of your concern.
Come straight to my personal room.

466
02:22:31,152 --> 02:22:32,483
All right.

467
02:22:33,487 --> 02:22:38,481
I want to see your son-in-law
comes for marriage or a circus.

468
02:22:40,494 --> 02:22:42,485
- I hear he'll come in a chopper
- Yes.

469
02:22:42,830 --> 02:22:46,493
Let's see this spectacle
What's the victory of love?

470
02:22:53,441 --> 02:22:54,908
Who is it?

471
02:22:57,445 --> 02:22:58,776
Yes.

472
02:23:10,458 --> 02:23:11,925
I got your letter.

473
02:23:13,461 --> 02:23:16,453
Pooja told me about you.

474
02:23:18,466 --> 02:23:21,458
She never told me how you
helped her in the journey.

475
02:23:22,470 --> 02:23:25,962
Your daughter is good
at forgetting favours.

476
02:23:28,476 --> 02:23:32,469
Don't mistake me. I meant
she didn't tell me till lately.

477
02:23:33,481 --> 02:23:36,917
''According to her,
you should get your dues.''

478
02:23:38,486 --> 02:23:40,477
Really? Full dues?

479
02:23:41,489 --> 02:23:42,956
That's good news.

480
02:23:44,492 --> 02:23:46,756
How should it be
according to you?

481
02:23:47,428 --> 02:23:53,196
I don't know. Must see what
right you have over the cash.

482
02:23:55,102 --> 02:23:57,434
I wouldn't come here
if I had no right.

483
02:24:00,441 --> 02:24:03,433
''Here, it's the complete account.''

484
02:24:05,446 --> 02:24:07,846
- Is it in English?
- You're holding it upside down.

485
02:24:10,451 --> 02:24:12,112
Sorry once again.

486
02:24:36,477 --> 02:24:40,470
''Hotel rent Rs. 45, iron Rs. 2,
toothpaste 9.30 I mean 9.50.''

487
02:24:40,881 --> 02:24:43,475
''Tooth brush 3.25,
repairing car Rs. 75.''

488
02:24:43,884 --> 02:24:46,751
''1 cap Rs. 35, 1 shirt 45,
2 pants Rs. 235''

489
02:24:47,087 --> 02:24:48,645
''1 bag 135, 1 shirt 135.''

490
02:24:48,822 --> 02:24:50,414
1 girl er... lungi 37.

491
02:24:51,091 --> 02:24:52,422
Total Rs. 699.55.

492
02:24:53,427 --> 02:24:54,917
699.55?

493
02:24:56,430 --> 02:24:58,762
I even had to sell
my socks and shaving kit.

494
02:24:59,099 --> 02:25:00,430
I haven't charged for that.

495
02:25:00,834 --> 02:25:03,826
- That's fine but...
- What's it? This is less.

496
02:25:04,438 --> 02:25:06,906
One generally spends
a couple of 1000 on such trips.

497
02:25:07,441 --> 02:25:10,433
Just a minute. First
explain this to me...

498
02:25:10,844 --> 02:25:14,439
You want Rs. 699.55
apart from Rs. 100000?

499
02:25:15,449 --> 02:25:16,848
What lakh?

500
02:25:18,452 --> 02:25:21,444
- The reward.
- I didn't speak of that.

501
02:25:23,057 --> 02:25:26,720
I'm confused. Have you
come for the reward?

502
02:25:26,961 --> 02:25:29,930
I've only come for 699.55

503
02:25:30,464 --> 02:25:32,728
Pay up fast. I'm
getting suffocated here.

504
02:25:34,468 --> 02:25:36,060
You're quite a man.

505
02:25:37,471 --> 02:25:41,965
- We'll discuss it another day.
- Another man would come for a lakh.

506
02:25:42,476 --> 02:25:45,468
It's about principles.
You won't understand it.

507
02:25:46,480 --> 02:25:50,883
When somebody makes a fool of me
and I have to pay the price...

508
02:25:51,485 --> 02:25:52,747
I don't accept that.

509
02:25:52,886 --> 02:25:54,478
Fool...?

510
02:25:55,889 --> 02:25:57,481
I was made a good fool.

511
02:26:00,160 --> 02:26:02,492
- Will you pay or must I leave?
- Just a minute.

512
02:26:06,500 --> 02:26:07,899
Rs. 700

513
02:26:10,504 --> 02:26:12,165
- What's this?
- 45 paise.

514
02:26:16,510 --> 02:26:17,977
One moment.

515
02:26:19,246 --> 02:26:20,907
May I ask you one question?

516
02:26:21,515 --> 02:26:23,005
Yes.

517
02:26:26,520 --> 02:26:28,010
Do you love my daughter?

518
02:26:32,526 --> 02:26:37,520
Any man who loves your daughter
should get his head examined.

519
02:26:40,200 --> 02:26:41,531
That's not the answer.

520
02:26:42,536 --> 02:26:45,027
Your daughter has found
herself a good match.

521
02:26:47,074 --> 02:26:49,474
A strange specimen of today's times.

522
02:26:51,211 --> 02:26:55,477
Your daughter needs a man
who'll thrash her day and night.

523
02:26:57,217 --> 02:26:59,947
''Lf you had any sense, you'd
have done this a lot earlier.''

524
02:27:02,489 --> 02:27:03,979
Do you love my daughter?

525
02:27:05,492 --> 02:27:09,223
No simple man can live
with her and not turn mad.

526
02:27:09,830 --> 02:27:11,491
I want nothing to do with her.

527
02:27:11,832 --> 02:27:13,231
Do you love her?

528
02:27:13,901 --> 02:27:17,496
Yes but I can't be blamed.

529
02:27:19,506 --> 02:27:20,837
I too am crazy.

530
02:27:39,526 --> 02:27:41,517
- Hope you've got the money.
- Right.

531
02:27:43,530 --> 02:27:45,930
- Congratulations.
- To you too.

532
02:27:46,533 --> 02:27:47,898
Won't you stay for the wedding?

533
02:27:48,469 --> 02:27:52,269
It will be fun. You probably
would never have seen it.

534
02:27:55,743 --> 02:27:57,870
I don't like watching dramas.

535
02:28:03,484 --> 02:28:05,816
- I spoke to Raghu.
- I don't want to hear a word.

536
02:28:06,487 --> 02:28:10,150
- Listen...
- I don't want to hear a word.

537
02:28:13,494 --> 02:28:14,961
But...

538
02:28:56,470 --> 02:28:58,199
''Come, my dear.''

539
02:29:15,489 --> 02:29:19,823
You're making a big
mistake marrying this man.

540
02:29:24,498 --> 02:29:26,159
Raghu is a good boy.

541
02:29:26,900 --> 02:29:29,494
He didn't come for the reward.

542
02:29:30,504 --> 02:29:32,836
He wanted the money he spent on you.

543
02:29:36,910 --> 02:29:40,505
Leave this marriage and run away.

544
02:29:41,915 --> 02:29:46,784
I'm probably the first father
to advise his child to elope.

545
02:29:49,456 --> 02:29:52,448
Before Raghu runs
away from your life...

546
02:29:53,193 --> 02:29:55,855
Sit in the car I've
parked behind and go away.

547
02:29:57,130 --> 02:29:59,189
Your father's honour is at stake.

548
02:30:07,474 --> 02:30:11,240
How can you marry such an ass?

549
02:31:26,486 --> 02:31:31,480
My heart won't pay heed

550
02:31:42,502 --> 02:31:48,907
Why am I feeling anxious?

551
02:31:50,177 --> 02:31:53,442
The heart is unaware

552
02:32:02,456 --> 02:32:05,914
- What's wrong?
- How can I marry an ass like you?

553
02:32:07,127 --> 02:32:08,458
What are you doing?

554
02:32:12,466 --> 02:32:15,458
''Run away, dear! ''

555
02:32:24,478 --> 02:32:28,141
''Stop, where are you going?
What is wrong with you? ''

556
02:32:29,483 --> 02:32:31,474
Run away!

557
02:32:39,993 --> 02:32:41,483
What's going on?
Where has Pooja gone?

558
02:32:42,496 --> 02:32:45,897
She's always running away
so she ran away again!

559
02:33:01,448 --> 02:33:02,938
I want to go to Bombay.

560
02:33:03,183 --> 02:33:04,844
Will you please help me?

561
02:33:15,796 --> 02:33:20,460
God always gives generously.

562
02:33:26,473 --> 02:33:31,467
I love you

563
02:33:33,480 --> 02:33:37,143
That's all I know

564
02:33:41,488 --> 02:33:47,825
I couldn't have lived alone

565
02:33:49,162 --> 02:33:52,427
Had I not found you...

566
02:33:56,770 --> 02:34:02,709
''Distressed eyes,
anxious breath... ''

567
02:34:04,444 --> 02:34:07,436
repeatedly say...

568
02:34:11,451 --> 02:34:15,444
My heart does not understand

569
02:34:18,458 --> 02:34:22,952
My heart knows no reason

